---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<style>
  body {
    background: #F7F3F0 !important;
  }
</style>

<Layout 
	title="Contact Us | Hoogly"
	description="Get in touch with the Hoogly team. We're here to help you with any questions or feedback."
	type="website"
>
	<div style="background: #F7F3F0; width: 100vw; margin-left: calc(-50vw + 50%); padding-top: 6rem; padding-bottom: 3.5rem;">
		<section class="about-hero-modern" style="background: none; padding: 0; margin-bottom: 0; position: relative; overflow: visible; border-radius: 0;">
			<div class="container" style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1.5rem;">
				<div class="about-hero-modern-inner" style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; width: 100%; margin: 0 auto; position: relative; min-height: 480px;">
					<div style="flex: 1 1 0; max-width: 50%; padding-left: 24px !important; padding-right: 40px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; z-index: 2; position: relative; background: none;">
						<h1 style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-size: 2.8rem; font-weight: 400; color: #23221F; margin-bottom: 0; line-height: 1.13; text-align: left;">Contact Us</h1>
						<div style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-weight: 400; margin-top: 2.5rem; font-size: 1.18rem; color: #23221F; line-height: 1.6;">
							<p>If you need help using Hoogly, have a question about your account, or just want to share feedback, we're all ears. Whether it's a technical issue or something you're feeling stuck on, our team (and Venn AI) are here to help you find clarity.</p>
							<p>Send us an email at: <a href="mailto:support@hoogly.com" style="color: #FF7D61; text-decoration: underline;">support@hoogly.com</a></p>
							<p>Together, let's build a workplace where people feel connected, supported, and seen.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div style="flex: 1 1 0; max-width: 50%; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; justify-content: flex-end; position: relative; z-index: 3; background: none;">
						<img src="/images/about-us/Mission Header.jpg" alt="Contact Us" style="width: 100%; max-width: 800px; min-width: 420px; border-radius: 20px; object-fit: cover; object-position: center; margin: 0; box-shadow: none; position: relative; top: 0; right: 0;" />
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</div>
</Layout> 